The announced card is as follows:

International Eliminator Tournament Match: Wildcard vs. The Beast Mortos

International Eliminator Tournament Match: Orange Cassidy vs. Hechicero

Willow Nightingale vs. Penelope Ford

We’ll hear from Kenny Omega, Will Ospreay, MJF, and Timeless Toni Storm

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fa4c6093-21b6-456d-8b2e-a7de9955c41f/20250312_170932.jpg)

Kenny Omega can't believe he's a singles champion in 2025. Omega thanks the people who supported him up until now but also KONOSUKE TAKESHITA for pushing him as hard as he did.

Kenny says Takeshita was truly an international champion, taking his belt around the world. Omega is glad to follow his lead by defending the belt against anyone from anywhere. Starting with this AEW Dynasty International Championship #1 Contender’s tournament.

Omega leaves and runs into SHIBATA on the ramp, who is in the tournament.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3ab13acb-bec9-4e76-82e4-540f4121fa1c/20250312_170926.jpg)

