"NOBODY SWINGS LIKE TONI STORM, SO LADIES PUT YOUR KEYS IN THE BOWL AND LETS GET THIS O\*GY STARTED!"

Toni Storm has lost a part of her heart forever but when she looks at the World Championship, she knows it was worth it.

Toni has officially called out everyone in the AEW Women's Locker Room and as she leaves, she's attacked by Megan Bayne.

