SPEEDBALL MIKE BAILEY IS THE WILD CARD!!!!!!

SPEEDBALL MIKE BAILEY HAS FINALLY ARRIVED IN AEW!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a98c452a-8c86-40a4-bd38-b0325ae2eaf2/20250312_180149.jpg)

*   ## **_SPEEDBALL MIKE BAILEY DEF. BEAST MORTOS TO ADVANCE TO THE FATAL FOUR WAY FOR #1 CONTENDERSHIP FOR THE INTERNATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9a6df12e-42d4-4b9b-b702-020153052b07/Screenshot_20250312_180943.jpg)

MJF punched a mirror as he insulted himself for losing to Hangman Page at the PPV 💔

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1b595af1-6e07-424b-ade7-654c038fe933/20250312_181135.jpg)

MJF is complaining about losing to Hangman when he's interrupted by MVP.

MVP and MJF hug each other and MVP tells a story of being proud of MJF for accomplishing everything he said he would when they first met eight years ago.

MVP says he doesn't appreciate MJF out here complaining when he used to be feared. Nobody in the locker room respects him. He needs the Hurt Syndicate. MVP says he wants to help MJF.

MJF refuses his offer at first. Reminding MVP that he used to be World Champion.

MJF tells MJF to focus on the word “WAS" and hands him the Hurt Syndicate business card again. MJF accepts the card 👀

