*   ## **_WILLOW NIGHTENGALE DEF. PENELOPE FORD_**
    

Post match Kris Statlander runs out to save Willow from a sneak attack from Penelope Ford. Megan Bayne comes back out and attacks Kris and Willow. Laying them both out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3be5403d-915d-43d2-8ef8-0c5cf7fee891/Screenshot_20250312_185001.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a7155321-f25e-4632-a71e-930dd7f3e0db/20250312_184946.jpg)

Mercedes Moné vs Billie Starks is set for next week!

A dream come true for the young up and coming Starks

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dc5228f9-dacc-4522-a443-4125c4257ae5/20250312_184941.jpg)

WILL OSPREAY HAS CALLED HIS SHOT!! WILL OSPREAY WANTS THE MAIN EVENT OF ALL IN FOR THE WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP!!!

Ospreay has officially entered the Owen Hart Cup

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9efe047a-2c19-4316-ba92-7ab037e52617/20250312_185512.jpg)

Hangman and MJF have run into each other again. Hangman says at Revolution he saw MJF's mask slip off. MJF cares what the people think, no matter what he says.

MJF tells Hangman he saw his mask slip off as well. No matter how much they cheer him, Hangman will never believe he's worth their love.

MJF says Hangman is going to do what he does best, he'll climb the mountain and just before he reaches the top. Hangman's self doubt will crush him and he will fall back down the mountain.

While MJF will climb that mountain to become World Champion over and over and over again.

Hangman says they will see... And it appears the rivals will go their separate ways for now.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f305c4ee-b457-43b8-9f30-db54c99e4cde/processed_20250312_191058.jpg)

*   ## **_ORANGE CASSIDY DEF. HECHICERO_**
    

Very fun and technical match that ends with Orange Cassidy cradling HECHICERO for the win. Post match, Mike Bailey comes out to stare down OC and close the show.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/88ee9624-13d5-48ff-9797-222df369c773/20250312_191103.jpg)